We see from the table that a majority of the time the model will classify someone as having a less income of \(50000 but that's likely because of the biased data that it was trained with you can find the shiny app here. where you can test to see if you meet its requirements to have an income above 50,000\) the shiny app was exported to shiny.io by saving the model object in a file and read on the server side of the app https://www.shinyapps.io/admin/#/application/722712
